        "story_pre": "Our Story",
        "story_heading": "Born from Ancient Ritual",
        "story_text": "<p>For centuries, the art of incense-making has been a sacred tradition in India \u2014 a bridge between the earthly and the divine. Each Anand Rasa incense stick carries that lineage forward.</p><p>We work with artisans who have inherited this craft through generations, using only botanicals that nature intended to be burned in devotion.</p>",
        "scent_pre": "Scent Profile",
        "scent_top": "Rose, Jasmine, Mogra",
        "scent_heart": "Sandalwood, Havan Samagri",
        "scent_base": "Pure Resin, Amber, Earth",
        "scent_desc_pre": "The Experience",
        "scent_desc": "<h3>A Fragrance That Stills the Mind</h3><p>Close your eyes. The first curl of smoke rises \u2014 soft, warm, botanical. The room shifts. What was ordinary becomes sacred.</p><p>This is what Anand Rasa incense does. It doesn't just scent a space. It changes the quality of the air. The quality of thought. The quality of being.</p>",
        "ritual_pre": "The Ritual",
        "ritual_heading": "A Practice of Presence",
